<subSubSection pageId="30" pageNumber="31" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="30.[151,1436,764,935]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,322,800,827]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
The smallest known species of 
<taxonomicName authority="Ruta, 2019" authorityName="Ruta" authorityYear="2019" box="[697,840,801,827]" class="Insecta" family="Scirtidae" genus="Calvariopsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis box="[697,840,801,827]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Calvariopsis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[850,955,801,827]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" rank="genus">gen. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
(TL 
<quantity box="[1017,1110,801,827]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.7" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" unit="mm" value="1.7">1.7 mm</quantity>
), round, blackish, externally resembling 
<taxonomicName authority="Ruta, 2019" authorityName="Ruta" authorityYear="2019" box="[283,466,837,863]" class="Insecta" family="Scirtidae" genus="Calvariopsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bituberculata" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[283,466,837,863]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">C. bituberculata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[474,564,837,863]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[474,564,837,863]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
Tergite VIII similar to that of 
<taxonomicName authority="(Pic)" authorityName="Ruta" authorityYear="2019" baseAuthorityName="Pic" baseAuthorityYear="1916" box="[907,1125,837,864]" class="Insecta" family="Scirtidae" genus="Calvariopsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="brasiliense">
<emphasis box="[907,1063,837,863]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">C. brasiliense</emphasis>
(Pic)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Ruta, 2019" authorityName="Ruta" authorityYear="2019" box="[1180,1332,837,863]" class="Insecta" family="Scirtidae" genus="Calvariopsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="guyanense" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[1180,1332,837,863]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">C. guyanense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1339,1429,837,863]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1339,1429,837,863]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
, apical plate with shallow V-shaped emargination flanked with two spine-like processes, covered with setae on posterolateral angles.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
